---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Base title="About" description="About the Cabinet collection.">
    <Header currentPage="about" />
    <main class="about-page">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h1>Cabinet</h1>
            <p>
                This site presents a personal collection of prints and drawings
                assembled by <a href="https://chrisgroskopf.com"
                    >Chris Groskopf</a
                > beginning in 2016. The collection includes European and American
                works spanning the sixteenth through twentieth centuries, with an
                emphasis on etching.
            </p>
            <p>
                The collection is primarily <em>opportunistic</em>. While parts
                of it reflect an interest in particular artists, such as <a
                    href="https://colmanetchings.com">Samuel Colman</a
                >, the majority is comprised of works I was lucky to find at an
                affordable price.
            </p>
            <p>
                Despite their modest origins, some of these works are quite
                rare, including a few of which I haven't been able to locate any
                other copies. I am publishing my collection to make these works
                accessible to researchers, collectors, and anyone else who may
                be interested in them.
            </p>
            <p>
                For inquiries, please email <a
                    href="mailto:chrisgroskopf@gmail.com"
                    >chrisgroskopf@gmail.com</a
                >. While I am not an art dealer, I will entertain thoughtful
                buy/sell/trade offers.
            </p>
            <p>
                This website is <a href="https://github.com/onyxfish/cabinet"
                    >open source</a
                > under the MIT license. It was created with <a
                    href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a
                > and is hosted on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/"
                    >Cloudflare Pages</a
                >. All content, including the photos, is licensed under the <a
                    href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/"
                    >Creative Commons BY-NC 4.0 license</a
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
</Base>

<style>
    .about-page {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 64px 32px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin: 0 0 20px;
    }

    p {
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 24px;
    }

    a {
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-lt);
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }
</style>
